# Generated JSON files - these are BUILD ARTIFACTS, not source files
# DO NOT commit JSON files to git - commit the source files instead:
#
# Source Type 1: Jsonnet sources (preferred workflow)
#   - Source: dashboards/sources/*.jsonnet + dashboards/components/*.libsonnet + dashboards/lib/*.libsonnet
#   - Build: jsonnet dashboards/sources/my_dashboard.jsonnet > dashboards/templates/my_dashboard.json
#   - Examples: asana.json, demo.json, ec2.json, github_cicd.json, skypilot_jobs.json
#
# Source Type 2: Python-generated (for complex visualizations)
#   - Source: scripts/generate_*.py
#   - Build: uv run python scripts/generate_health_grid.py
#   - Examples: system_health_rollup.json, system_health_rollup_wildcard.json
#
dashboards/templates/*.json

